        <para id="id4098888">Compound nouns</para>
        <para id="id4098893">In English we can use nouns as adjectives. For example:</para>
        <para id="id4098898">Water sportStork sanctuaryAdventure tour</para>
        <para id="id4098910">The relationship between the two nouns can be of many kinds, including:</para>
        <para id="id4098915">Place:mountain slopes, city center</para>
        <para id="id4098930">Time:summer holiday, weekend break</para>
        <para id="id4098946">Function:golf course, swimming pool</para>
        <para id="id4098960">Material:paper bag, iron bridge, stone cathedral</para>
