        <para id="id4099163">Advice and suggestions</para>
        <para id="id4099168">We can give advice to someone by using the following structures.</para>
        <list id="id4099173" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>If you’re looking for …….., then go to ………</item>
          <item>Don’t miss ………</item>
          <item>…….. is a must for any visitors to ……..(city).</item>
          <item>You can’t leave ….. (city) without ……</item>
        </list>
